TITLE: KN95 Masks - Box Of 50 Masks
DESCRIPTION: ['Box of 50 KN95 masks\xa0', "\ufeffThis\xa0product is\xa0the perfect\xa0choice for following the government's advice for non-medical face coverings in certain shops, general workplace protection and public transport etc. allowing the medical standard products to be reserved for those that need it most, our front line and key workers.", 'Hygienically sealed and wrapped in 5 packs of 10 masks per box.', 'These Masks Meet EU Standard EN 149:2001+A1:2009.', 'KN95 masks have a minimum filtration efficiency of 95%.', 'Adjustable nose clip to improve adaptability and fit.', 'KN95 masks are very durable in comparison to the traditional rectangle ear loop masks.', 'The 3D Design structure makes for a very comfortable fit, with the mask held slightly away from the mouth to allow more room for comfortable breathing and speaking.', 'The 3D folding design of the mask also allows the mask to be folded flat for easy travel storage purposes.', 'Inner layer is skin friendly non woven fabric, soft and comfortable.', 'These masks are not designed to be washed.', '\xa0']
